data.description: Discover the epitome of luxurious living in this exquisite 5 bdrm, 2.5-bath home with office, nestled within a sought-after Peoria neighborhood. Boasting an expansive open floor plan, this residence invites you to indulge in spacious comfort and modern elegance. The heart of the home, a generously-sized kitchen with 48'' cabinetry and a sprawling island, is a chef's dream. Executive vanities and tile floors grace the stylish bathrooms. Cozy up by the fireplace, entertain in the inviting living areas. Step into the serene backyard oasis, complete with  pergolas, perfect for unwinding or hosting gatherings. Placed on an extra-large corner lot at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. This is the perfect time to make this your dream home.
